title: Levi's Women's 501 90s Jeans
description: Runs large; designed for a loose fit. For a higher and closer fit, size down, Intended for a mid rise with a straight leg fit. Non-stretch denim will soften and give with wear.
Leather logo patch at back, Faded wash and distressed cuffs
The iconic Levi's 501 jeans, updated with a loose, '90s-inspired fit and mid rise. These straight-leg jeans boast a faded wash and just-right distressing for a well-loved, vintage appeal.
